properties.areaDesc: Coastal Waters from Schoodic Point, ME to Stonington, ME out 25 NM; Coastal Waters from Eastport, ME to Schoodic Point, ME out 25 NM
properties.headline: Storm Warning issued February 7 at 2:38PM EST until February 8 at 1:00AM EST by NWS Caribou ME
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds 40 to 50 kt with gusts up to 60 kt and
seas 16 to 21 feet expected.

* WHERE...Coastal Waters from Eastport, ME to Schoodic Point, ME
out 25 NM and Coastal Waters from Schoodic Point, ME to
Stonington, ME out 25 NM.

* WHEN...Until 1 AM EST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Very strong winds will cause hazardous seas which
could capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should remain in port, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: STORM WARNING IN EFFECT UNTIL 1 AM EST SATURDAY
